主要翻译
 
specify [sth] # vtr (state exactly)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 明确说明 míng què shuō míng TC Traditional Chinese 明確說明  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 详细说明 míng què shuō míng，xiáng xì shuō míng TC Traditional Chinese 詳細說明 
 -- John specified that the article only related to the small region he had visited and not the whole country.

其他翻译
 
specify [sth] vtr (state as requirement)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 规定 guī dìng TC Traditional Chinese 規定  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 指定 guī dìng，zhǐ dìng TC Traditional Chinese 指定 
 -- The company specified that only applicants with a relevant bachelor's degree would be considered for the post.

